g.text: a) Do not remove the plastic retainer prior to installation.
Doing so may cause the steel balls to fall out.
b) Install the linear bearing onto the right rail
by aligning the plastic retainer against the rail end.
c) Pay attention not to tilt the C beam
after bearing installation as it may fall out

ShowToolTip(evt,'10',"0247_M4X6 socket Button head cap screw Black")
